#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipe.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.ellipe"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:1 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "第二类完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:3 of
msgid "This function is defined as"
msgstr "该函数定义为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"E(m) = \\int_0^{\\pi/2} [1 - m \\sin(t)^2]^{1/2} dt\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipe.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:7 of
msgid "Defines the parameter of the elliptic integral."
msgstr "定义椭圆积分的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:9 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipe.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:12 of
msgid "**E** -- Value of the elliptic integral."
msgstr "**E** -- 椭圆积分的值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipe.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipkm1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:18 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind, near `m` = 1"
msgstr "第一类完全椭圆积分，接近 `m` = 1"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipk`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:21 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind"
msgstr "第一类完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipkinc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:24 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the first kind"
msgstr "第一类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipeinc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:27 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "第二类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprd`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:30 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:33 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:37 of
msgid "Wrapper for the Cephes [1]_ routine `ellpe`."
msgstr "Cephes [1]_ 例程 `ellpe` 的封装。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:39 of
msgid "For ``m > 0`` the computation uses the approximation,"
msgstr "对于 ``m > 0``，计算使用近似，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:41 of
msgid ""
"E(m) \\approx P(1-m) - (1-m) \\log(1-m) Q(1-m),\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:43 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`P` and :math:`Q` are tenth-order polynomials.  For ``m < "
"0``, the relation"
msgstr "其中 :math:`P` 和 :math:`Q` 是十次多项式。对于 ``m < 0``，使用关系式"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:46 of
msgid ""
"E(m) = E(m/(m - 1)) \\sqrt(1-m)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:48 of
msgid "is used."
msgstr "进行计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:50 of
msgid ""
"The parameterization in terms of :math:`m` follows that of section 17.2 "
"in [2]_. Other parameterizations in terms of the complementary parameter "
":math:`1 - m`, modular angle :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m`, or modulus "
":math:`k^2 = m` are also used, so be careful that you choose the correct "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"以 :math:`m` 为参数的参数化遵循 [2]_ 中第 17.2 节的形式。其他以余参数 :"
"math:`1 - m`、模角 :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m` 或模数 :math:`k^2 = m` 为"
"参数的参数化方式也常被使用，因此请确保选择正确的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:56 of
msgid ""
"The Legendre E integral is related to Carlson's symmetric R_D or R_G "
"functions in multiple ways [3]_. For example,"
msgstr ""
"Legendre E 积分与 Carlson 对称 R_D 或 R_G 函数在多种方式下相关 [3]_。例如"
"，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipe:59 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"E(m) = 2 R_G(0, 1-k^2, 1) .\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"E(m) = 2 R_G(0, 1-k^2, 1) 。\n"
"\n"

